me they're guests of yours.

01:01:44.100 --> 01:01:48.930
One of them is Spike and the other
one, Razor, where would you like me

01:01:48.930 --> 01:01:52.430
to put them, pray tell,
Machito, where will I seat them?

01:01:52.430 --> 01:01:54.250
Next to the Duchess of York?

01:01:54.250 --> 01:01:58.340
I don't think so, I don't think,
maybe with the Earl of Cambridge,

01:01:58.340 --> 01:02:02.700
that might be better for me, yeah,
put them where, and they'd go nuts.

01:02:02.700 --> 01:02:04.000
They'd love it.

01:02:04.000 --> 01:02:05.370
Because our music is aggressive.

01:02:05.370 --> 01:02:09.720
And when he would seat them,
it became more aggressive.

01:02:09.720 --> 01:02:15.220
So he could connect with the
audience, whatever it might be,

01:02:15.220 --> 01:02:18.780
you know, whether young or old or
whatever their musical taste was

01:02:18.780 --> 01:02:23.090 position:56%
at the moment, he could turn them
around for that hour or so of music,

01:02:23.090 --> 01:02:26.890
which is, I got to, I can't
do that kind of stuff.

01:02:26.890 --> 01:02:28.190
But he could.

01:02:28.190 --> 01:02:29.490
Certainly.

01:02:29.490 --> 01:02:32.000
&gt;&gt; Larry Applebaum: Who
else has a question?

01:02:32.000 --> 01:02:33.440
Surely.

01:02:33.440 --> 01:02:37.100
&gt;&gt; Well, then I will
ask, maybe a couple more.

01:02:37.100 --> 01:02:41.060
And one is, after he was
established in New York,

01:02:41.060 --> 01:02:43.700
he became this big
star of the music.

01:02:43.700 --> 01:02:45.120
Did he ever go back to the island?

01:02:45.120 --> 01:02:46.420
&gt;&gt; Mario Grillo: Never.

01:02:46.420 --> 01:02:47.720
Never went back to Cuba.

01:02:47.720 --> 01:02:50.540
As a matter of fact there
was a big stink about that.

01:02:50.540 --> 01:02:56.100
We were in London and the
ambassador of Cuba to London came

01:02:56.100 --> 01:02:58.430
down to Ronnie's and said
Machito, you know what?

01:02:58.430 --> 01:02:59.730
We want to bring you to Cuba.

01:02:59.730 --> 01:03:01.030
He said, no man.

01:03:01.030 --> 01:03:02.530
Thanks, but no thanks.

01:03:02.530 --> 01:03:03.830
Never went back.

01:03:03.830 --> 01:03:09.330 position:56%
Puerto Rico, Venezuela,
[inaudible] Peru, yes, fine, but no,

01:03:09.330 --> 01:03:13.040
he never went back to Cuba.

01:03:13.040 --> 01:03:19.410 position:56%
Now, now that relations have
changed somewhat over the last year,

01:03:19.410 --> 01:03:25.880
and down the road, I think
it would be spectacular

01:03:25.880 --> 01:03:29.340
to take the Machito
Orchestra to Cuba.

01:03:29.340 --> 01:03:33.140
I think that would
be quite something.

01:03:33.140 --> 01:03:37.030
But, on the flip side of that,
where we would play the carnivals

01:03:37.030 --> 01:03:40.100
