play, how many of them you got?

01:03:58.720 --> 01:04:02.380
I said, man, like a thousand.

01:04:02.380 --> 01:04:05.140
He goes, and they're all like that?

01:04:05.140 --> 01:04:07.840
I said, yeah.

01:04:07.840 --> 01:04:11.700
He said, we've never
heard this music in Cuba.

01:04:13.110 --> 01:04:17.880
We, we, you know, I haven't heard
you play the same tune twice,

01:04:17.880 --> 01:04:22.390
