how is that, how is that possible?

01:04:22.390 --> 01:04:25.920
I said, yo, my man, it would take
like another 25 days for me to run

01:04:25.920 --> 01:04:32.790
out of things that I'm playing
for the first time, you know?

01:04:32.790 --> 01:04:38.810
The book is deep, it's
very deep and very varied.

01:04:38.810 --> 01:04:40.940
Machito recorded albums,
I was telling you,

01:04:40.940 --> 01:04:45.230
Machito goes to Memphis, where
he recorded Knock on Wood

01:04:45.230 --> 01:04:49.060
