things like that, Alphie,

01:04:49.060 --> 01:04:53.790
there's a Machito Plays Irving
Berlin, there's An Affair

01:04:53.790 --> 01:04:58.480 position:56%
to Remember, he did another one, the
Sun Also Rises based on Hemingway.

01:04:58.480 --> 01:05:01.890
And so the book is very diverse.

01:05:01.890 --> 01:05:06.860
So that, that's a good thing
for me because I have option

01:05:06.860 --> 01:05:10.030
