01:07:02.220 --> 01:07:04.400
Well, that's very nice.

01:07:04.400 --> 01:07:06.580
And whose little girl are you?

01:07:06.580 --> 01:07:07.880
She says him, him.

01:07:07.880 --> 01:07:09.180
He says, oh, Mario.

01:07:09.180 --> 01:07:12.070
