part of the club man.

01:08:06.870 --> 01:08:08.170
Don't think that way.

01:08:08.170 --> 01:08:14.080
And I'm like, whoa,
okay, part of the club.

01:08:14.080 --> 01:08:15.710
I didn't know.

01:08:15.710 --> 01:08:17.330
Thanks for telling me.

