listening, listening, listening.

01:08:33.120 --> 01:08:34.950
And I'm you know, I'm
having, you know,

01:08:34.950 --> 01:08:37.000
this phobia to learn this material.

01:08:37.000 --> 01:08:39.320
So then we get to the concert,
we play the concert without,

01:08:39.320 --> 01:08:41.520
we come back stage,
who's back stage?

01:08:41.520 --> 01:08:46.900
Max Roach, Elvin Jones,
Billy Higgins, Louis Hayes,

01:08:46.900 --> 01:08:53.650 position:56%
Jack DeJohnette, the most incredible
drummers on the face of the earth.

01:08:53.650 --> 01:08:56.930
