01:08:56.930 --> 01:08:59.770
at me, he goes, you know what,
you know what, Mario man?

01:08:59.770 --> 01:09:01.070
[Inaudible] Dizzy.

01:09:01.070 --> 01:09:04.850
He said, you said you the
greatest drummer I ever played

01:09:04.850 --> 01:09:06.150
